### Create a new habit
POST http://localhost:3000/api/habits
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Morning Jog",
  "description": "Jog for 30 minutes",
  "frequency": "daily",
  "userId": "6842038aecd9d47a2a9ae467"
}

### Get all habits (optional: filter by userId)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/habits/all

### Get a single habit by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/habits/6842039cecd9d47a2a9ae46a

### Update a habit by ID
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/habits/6842039cecd9d47a2a9ae46a
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Dinner Time Walk",
  "description": "Walk instead of jogging",
  "frequency": "daily"
}

### Delete a habit by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/habits/6842039cecd9d47a2a9ae46a